      "id": "e5763938-d189-405e-acdd-bdac440fffeb",
      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soient $a_1,\\dots,a_n \\in  K$ distincts et $P = (X-a_1)\\dots(X-a_n)$.",
        "html": "<p>Soient <span class=\"math inline\">\\(a_1,\\dots,a_n \\in  K\\)</span>\ndistincts et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(P =\n(X-a_1)\\dots(X-a_n)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "883dc5fd-813a-4b46-a41f-ecd0eabbf77e",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "D{\\'e}composer en {\\'e}l{\\'e}ments simples la fraction $\\frac {(1+X^2)^n}{P^2}$.",
        "html": "<p>D<span>é</span>composer en <span>é</span>l<span>é</span>ments simples\nla fraction <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac\n{(1+X^2)^n}{P^2}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "d1a77f4f-4b7b-4035-af84-2502a7f982bd",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Montrer que les coefficients des $\\frac1{X-a_i}$ sont tous nuls si et seulement si :\n    $(1+X^2)P'' - 2nXP' + n(n+1)P = 0$.",
        "html": "<p>Montrer que les coefficients des <span\nclass=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac1{X-a_i}\\)</span> sont tous nuls si et\nseulement si : <span class=\"math inline\">\\((1+X^2)P&#39;&#39; -\n2nXP&#39; + n(n+1)P = 0\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "15566a88-e332-444a-b09e-22bd81fdd067",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$\\sum_{i=1}^n \\Bigl( \\frac{(1+a_i^2)^n}{P'^2(a_i)(X-a_i)^2}\n             + \\frac{2na_i - P''(a_i)(1+a_i^2)/P'(a_i)}{P'^2(a_i)(X-a_i)} \\Bigr)$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\sum_{i=1}^n \\Bigl(\n\\frac{(1+a_i^2)^n}{P&#39;^2(a_i)(X-a_i)^2}\n             + \\frac{2na_i -\nP&#39;&#39;(a_i)(1+a_i^2)/P&#39;(a_i)}{P&#39;^2(a_i)(X-a_i)}\n\\Bigr)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
  ],
